## 🚫 HARD RULES
- NEVER use JUnit 4 annotations (@RunWith, org.junit.Test, etc.)
- NEVER use PowerMock
- NEVER leave empty test method bodies
- NEVER overwrite existing passing tests
- NEVER skip a class without logging why
- NEVER stop before attempting all 5 retries
- ALWAYS make each test fully independent — no shared mutable state between tests
- ALWAYS re-read the source file before fixing a test error
- ALWAYS prefer constructor injection in tests over field injection for clarity
